The '''2011–12 [[Cuban National Series]]''' was the 51st edition of the tournament. It began on Sunday, November 28 with a game between [[Ciego de Avila (baseball)|Ciego de Avila]] and [[Pinar del Río]], with Villa Clara winning 6-5. The All-Star Game was played on February 24, 2011. The regular season finished on March 24.
