'''Aguada Coliseum''' is an arena in [[Aguada, Puerto Rico]].  It hosted some of the judo and wrestling events for the [[2010 Central American and Caribbean Games]].<ref>http://www.mayaguez2010.com/es/instalaciones/deportivas/247-coliseo-aguada.html</ref>

