'''Estádio Universitário São Paulo''' is a multi-use [[stadium]] located in [[São Paulo]], [[Brazil]]. It is used mostly for [[football (soccer)|football]] matches and hosts the home matches of [[University of São Paulo]]. It was built in 1954.<ref name="world">{{cite web |url=http://www.worldstadiums.com/south_america/countries/brazil/sao_paulo.shtml |title=Stadiums in Brazil: São Paulo |publisher=World Stadiums |accessdate=May 9, 2016}}</ref> The stadium has a capacity of 30,000 people.<ref name="world"/>

