{{Use dmy dates|date=March 2015}} {{Infobox sportsperson | name = Francis Bonafede | birth_name = | fullname = | nationality = | residence = | birth_date = {{birth date and age|1939|7|14|df=yes}} | birth_place = [[Monaco]] | death_date = | death_place = | height = | weight = | website = | country = | sport = [[Shooting sport|Sports shooting]] | event = | medaltemplates = | show-medals = yes }}
'''Francis Bonafede''' (born 14 July 1939) is a [[Monaco|Monegasque]] [[Shooting sport|sports shooter]]. He competed in the [[Shooting at the 1960 Summer Olympics – Men's trap|trap event]] at the [[1960 Summer Olympics]].<ref name="sportsref">{{cite web|url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/bo/francis-bonafede-1.html |title=Francis Bonafede |accessdate=10 July 2015 |work=Sports Reference |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150613151733/http://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/bo/francis-bonafede-1.html |archivedate=13 June 2015 |df=dmy }}</ref>
